      "type": "code",
      "lang": "javascript",
      "content": "function criarCarrinho() {\n  const itens = [];\n\n  function adicionar(nome, qtd) {\n    itens.push({ nome, qtd });\n  }\n\n  function totalItens() {\n    let t = 0;\n    for (const it of itens) {\n      t = t + it.qtd;\n    }\n    return t;\n  }\n\n  return { adicionar, totalItens };\n}\n\nconst carrinho = criarCarrinho();\ncarrinho.adicionar('Arroz', 2);\ncarrinho.adicionar('Café', 1);\nconsole.log(carrinho.totalItens()); // 3",
